plot: A colorful and foul-mouthed feature musical comedy.A film about a frizzy-haired, pink-cheeked outcast named Spork who is trying to navigate her way through the annals of junior high. When a school dance show provides a chance for Spork to show up a mean girls gang, her trailer-park neighbor steps up to coach her with some &"booty-poppin&" moves. Featuring a vintage 90's soundtrack (that includes 2-Live Crew, JJ Fad's &"SuperSonic,&" Dimples T's &"Get It Girl&"), a score by Casey James and the Stay Puft Kid; and extended school hall dance sequences, Spork is a film about standing out and fitting in.   Written by  Spork
